# Penguin Labs Capital Website

This is a modern, responsive website for Penguin Labs Capital, a venture capital firm. The website features:

## Design Principles
- Clean, minimalist design inspired by the LoveFrom website
- Penguin character as the central brand element
- Modern typography using Inter font family
- Smooth animations and interactive elements
- Professional color scheme with blue and orange accents

## Technologies Used
- Vanilla HTML5, CSS3, and JavaScript
- CSS Grid and Flexbox for layout
- CSS custom properties for theming
- Intersection Observer API for scroll animations
- SVG graphics for the penguin character

## Code Style Guidelines
- Use semantic HTML elements
- Follow BEM methodology for CSS class naming where applicable
- Use CSS custom properties for consistent theming
- Implement smooth transitions and animations
- Ensure responsive design for all screen sizes
- Add proper accessibility features (ARIA labels, semantic markup)

## Key Features
- Animated penguin SVG character
- Smooth scrolling navigation
- Fade-in animations on scroll
- Interactive hover effects
- Mobile-responsive design
- Parallax scrolling effects

When making changes, maintain the elegant and professional aesthetic while keeping the penguin theme central to the brand identity.
